OL,3,CPensioners protest on Chancellor's
OL,4,Cdoorstep over winter fuel payment
OL,6,FProtesters have gathered close to the
OL,7,FChancellor's constituency to oppose
OL,8,Fgovernment cuts to winter fuel
OL,9,Fpayments.
OL,11,FDozens of people took to the streets
OL,12,Fof Leeds city centre - a couple of
OL,13,Fmiles from Rachel Reeves' Leeds West
OL,14,Fand Pudsey constituency - after she
OL,15,Fannounced major changes to the
OL,16,Fallowance.
OL,18,FReeves continues to face intense
OL,19,Fcriticism over the decision to
OL,20,Fintroduce means testing for anyone
OL,21,Fclaiming the benefit.
