OL,3,CPensioners protest on Chancellor's
OL,4,Cdoorstep over winter fuel payment
OL,6,FThursday's protest, which took place
OL,7,Fat Dortmund Square, was the latest in
OL,8,Fa series of demonstrations by union
OL,9,FUnite and pensioners' groups.
OL,11,FJohn Randall, 86, was among those who
OL,12,Fgathered. He said pensioners should
OL,13,Fnot be targeted by the government as
OL,14,Fit seeks to save money.
OL,16,FHe said: "They should have another way
OL,17,Fof finding that money, they shouldn't
OL,18,Fstart from the bottom. Why don't they
OL,19,Fstart at the top."
