OL,3,CPensioners protest on Chancellor's
OL,4,Cdoorstep over winter fuel payment
OL,6,F"Everyone will be a pensioner if they
OL,7,Fare lucky, so anything that the
OL,8,Fpensioners lose now won't be there for
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,F"We are not greedy, we want enough to
OL,12,Flive and we want enough to survive."
OL,14,FFran Postlethwaite, secretary of the
OL,15,FYorkshire and Humber Pensioners
OL,16,FConvention, said vulnerable people
OL,17,Fwere at risk.
