OL,3,CPensioners protest on Chancellor's
OL,4,Cdoorstep over winter fuel payment
OL,6,FShe said: "The people who don't apply
OL,7,Ffor fuel payments that are entitled
OL,8,Fand the people who are just above will
OL,9,Fget absolutely nothing. They are the
OL,10,Fones who will suffer."
OL,12,FAccording to polling by Unite, just a
OL,13,Fthird of voters in Reeves' own
OL,14,Fconstituency supported the
OL,15,Fintroduction of means testing.
