OL,3,CPensioners protest on Chancellor's
OL,4,Cdoorstep over winter fuel payment
OL,6,FGeneral secretary Sharon Graham said:
OL,7,F"The campaign opposing the
OL,8,Fpickpocketing of pensioners is now
OL,9,Fcoming to the chancellor's own back
OL,10,Fyard. Her own constituents don't
OL,11,Fsupport the policy and neither does
OL,12,Fthe rest of the country.
OL,14,F"The government needs to rapidly
OL,15,Frethink this tin-eared cut. It is
OL,16,Fsimply wrong that Winter Fuel Payments
OL,17,Fhave been slashed while the mega
OL,18,Fwealthy remain untouched."
